features: ❋High-Speed Transmission: This external SSD adopts USB 3.0 interface, which greatly improves data transfer efficiency and ensures stable performance. The transmission speed can reach up to 5Gbps, allowing you to access your files in seconds.
❋Reliable Protection: Built-in multiple protection mechanisms including over-voltage, over-current, overheating and other protection to effectively protect the hard disk from damage.

❋Versatile Multi-Compatibility: Streamline your data backup and transfer process with an external SSD that supports multiple operating systems. Enjoy the convenience of effortless file access and sharing across different devices.

❋Seamless Performance: Experience dependable and speedy performance effortlessly with this external SSD. The screwless design allows for simple and easy installation and use without the need for any tools, providing a hassle-free setup.

❋Portable Convenience: With its lightweight and compact design, this external SSD is the perfect travel companion to store and transfer your important data anywhere, anytime. N0 more worrying about carrying bulky hard drives, this slim and portable SSD is easy to carry around.
